sentences: == 1999–2001 – new media pioneer –

Based in Los Angeles, in 1999, Eckstine became SVP/Creative Development, for the original online music service provider, MP3.com, providing artist development expertise on the MP3.com "Music and Technology Tour" featuring, Alanis Morissette, Tori Amos, Christina Aguilera, and TLC.
